question.string: Show me games by Wilhelm Steinitz.

query.sparql: SELECT DISTINCT ?game WHERE { ?game prop:white|prop:black 'Wilhelm Steinitz' .}

question.string: Show me all won games of Emanuel Lasker against Wilhelm Steinitz
question.keywords: Emanuel Lasker, Wilhelm Steinitz, won, games

query.sparql: SELECT DISTINCT ?game WHERE { {?game prop:black 'Wilhelm Steinitz' . ?game prop:white 'Emanuel Lasker' . ?game prop:result '1-0' . } UNION {?game prop:white 'Wilhelm Steinitz' . ?game prop:black 'Emanuel Lasker' . ?game prop:result '0-1' . } }

question.string: Which player with an ELO above 2500 has won most often in 1899?

query.sparql: SELECT ?player (count(?game) AS ?nr) WHERE { {?game prop:white ?player . ?game prop:result '1-0' . ?game prop:date ?date . ?game prop:whiteelo ?elo . FILTER regex(?date, '1899') } UNION {?game prop:black ?player . ?game prop:result '0-1' . ?game prop:date ?date . ?game prop:blackelo ?elo . FILTER regex(?date, '1899') } } GROUP BY ?player ?elo HAVING (?elo > 2500) ORDER BY DESC(?nr) LIMIT 1 OFFSET 0

question.string: Did Emanuel Lasker play the opening Kings Gambit?

query.sparql: ASK { ?game prop:black|prop:white 'Emanuel Lasker' . ?game prop:eco ?eco . FILTER regex(?eco, '^C3[0-9]{1}.*') }

question.string: Who did play blind games?

query.sparql: SELECT DISTINCT ?person WHERE { ?game prop:black|prop:white ?person . ?game prop:event ?event . FILTER regex(?event, 'blind', 'i') }

question.string: Show me endgames with rook against rook and pawn.

query.sparql: SELECT DISTINCT ?game WHERE { ?game prop:moves ?moves . ?moves prop:fen ?fen . FILTER (regex(?fen, '^[^BbNnQqP]* w|b ') && regex(?fen, '^[^p]+p{1}[^p]+ ') && regex(?fen, '^[^r]*r{1}[^r]* ') && regex(?fen, '^[^R]*R{1}[^R]* ')) }

question.string: In which tournaments did Adolf Anderssen and Wilhelm Steinitz play against each other?

query.sparql: SELECT DISTINCT ?event WHERE { ?game prop:black|prop:white 'Adolf Anderssen' . ?game prop:black|prop:white 'Wilhelm Steinitz' . ?game prop:event ?event . }

question.string: All losing games of Wilhelm Steinitz from London.

query.sparql: SELECT DISTINCT ?game WHERE { {?game prop:black 'Wilhelm Steinitz' . ?game prop:result '1-0' . ?game prop:site ?site . FILTER regex(?site, 'London', 'i') } UNION {?game prop:white 'Wilhelm Steinitz' . ?game prop:result '0-1' . ?game prop:site ?site . FILTER regex(?site, 'London', 'i') } }

question.string: Give me 5 games with an underpromotion.

query.sparql: SELECT DISTINCT ?game WHERE { ?game prop:moves ?moves . ?moves prop:move ?move . FILTER regex(?move, '[BNRbnr]$') } LIMIT 5 OFFSET 0

question.string: Show me all games of the world championship 1886.

query.sparql: SELECT DISTINCT ?game WHERE { ?game prop:event ?event . ?game prop:date ?date . FILTER (regex(?event, 'World Championship', 'i') && regex(?date, '1886', 'i')) }

question.string: What is the longest game?

query.sparql: SELECT DISTINCT ?game (MAX(?nr) AS ?max) WHERE { ?game prop:moves ?moves . ?moves prop:moveNr ?nr . } GROUP BY ?game ORDER BY DESC(?max) LIMIT 1 OFFSET 0

question.string: Give me games where Adolf Anderssen defeats Howard Staunton with black.
question.keywords: Adolf Anderssen, black, defeats, Howard Staunton

query.sparql: SELECT DISTINCT ?game WHERE { ?game prop:white 'Adolf Anderssen'. ?game prop:black 'Howard Staunton'. ?game prop:result '1-0'. }

question.string: What is the first game of Adolf Anderssen?

query.sparql: SELECT DISTINCT ?game WHERE { ?game prop:black|prop:white 'Adolf Anderssen' . ?game prop:date ?date . } ORDER BY ASC(?date) LIMIT 1 OFFSET 0

question.string: Show me games of white in the Evans Gambit

query.sparql: SELECT DISTINCT ?game WHERE { ?game cont:eco ?eco . ?eco cont:openingCode ?e . FILTER regex(?e, 'C5[1-2].*') }

question.string: Which opening has Wilhelm Steinitz played most frequently?

query.sparql: SELECT DISTINCT ?eco (COUNT(?eco) AS ?nr) WHERE { ?game prop:white|prop:black 'Wilhelm Steinitz' . ?game prop:eco ?eco . } GROUP BY ?eco ORDER BY DESC(?nr) LIMIT 1 OFFSET 0

question.string: In which game did Wilhelm Steinitz have his highest rating?

query.sparql: SELECT DISTINCT ?game WHERE { {?game prop:black 'Wilhelm Steinitz' . ?game prop:blackelo ?elo . } UNION {?game prop:white 'Wilhelm Steinitz' . ?game prop:whiteelo ?elo . } } ORDER BY DESC(?elo) LIMIT 1

question.string: Show me all the games of the tournament with the highest average rating.

query.sparql: SELECT DISTINCT ?game WHERE { ?game prop:event ?event . {SELECT DISTINCT ?event (AVG(xsd:integer(?elo)) AS ?avg) WHERE { ?game prop:event ?event . ?game prop:whiteelo|prop:blackelo ?elo . } GROUP BY ?event ORDER BY DESC(?avg) LIMIT 1 } }

question.string: Give me the games in which Wilhelm Steinitz lost against a much weaker player.

query.sparql: SELECT DISTINCT ?game WHERE { {?game prop:black 'Wilhelm Steinitz' . ?game prop:result '1-0' . ?game prop:whiteelo ?whiteelo . ?game prop:blackelo ?blackelo . FILTER (xsd:integer(?blackelo) > xsd:integer(?whiteelo)) } UNION {?game prop:white 'Wilhelm Steinitz' . ?game prop:result '0-1' . ?game prop:whiteelo ?whiteelo . ?game prop:blackelo ?blackelo . FILTER (xsd:integer(?blackelo) < xsd:integer(?whiteelo)) } }

question.string: What openings were played at the World Championship 1894?

question.string: Who was the 5th world champion?

query.sparql: SELECT DISTINCT ?player (COUNT(?result) + ((COUNT(?draw))/2) AS ?points) WHERE { {?game prop:black ?player . ?game prop:event '5. World Championship' . ?game prop:result '0-1' . ?game prop:result ?result . } UNION {?game prop:white ?player . ?game prop:event '5.
